      *--------------------------------------------------------*
      * STRTPROGRAM (EAER07)                                   *
      *--------------------------------------------------------*
     C                     SETOF                     020304
     C                     SETOF                     053233
     C                     Z-ADDIITKCD    PTOKU   40
     C                     Z-ADDIITANK    WTANK   92
     C                     Z-ADDIITANK    @@TANK  92
      ****日本スタッドの得意先変換と金額の計算****
     C           IITKCD    IFEQ 6440
     C           IINOU     ANDEQ6440
     C                     SETON                     32
     C                     MOVE 1005      PTOKU   40
     C           WTANK     MULT IINOSU    KINGK   92
     C                     END
      *
      **** T-6440 N-2399 -1-00の時（単価　金額）無印字 92.11.20 YAMA
     C           IITKCD    IFEQ 6440
     C           IINOU     ANDEQ2399
     C           IIKJCD    ANDEQ'1'
     C           IIUKCD    ANDEQ'00  '
     C                     SETOF                     32
     C                     SETON                     33
     C                     END
      **** T-7781 N-7781 -2-00の時（単価　金額）無印字 93.02.17 YAMA
